  "page": "Fair Isle rebellion",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#B0C4DE;\">Fair Isle rebellion</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a> expelled from Fair Isle<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Farman\" title=\"House Farman\">House Farman</a> restored to power</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"text-align:left; background:none\">\n  <tbody><tr><td width=\"50%\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Belligerents</td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">Smallfolk</a> of Fair Isle<br />\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Knights</a> of Fair Isle</td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\">Ironborn:\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Wynch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Wynch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ef/House_Wynch.svg/30px-House_Wynch.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ef/House_Wynch.svg/45px-House_Wynch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ef/House_Wynch.svg/60px-House_Wynch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wynch\" title=\"House Wynch\">House Wynch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Goodbrother.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/30px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/45px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/60px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Notable commanders</td></tr><tr><td>Unknown</td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Wynch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Wynch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ef/House_Wynch.svg/20px-House_Wynch.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ef/House_Wynch.svg/30px-House_Wynch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ef/House_Wynch.svg/40px-House_Wynch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Wynch\" title=\"Alester Wynch\">Alester Wynch</a>†<br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Goodbrother.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/20px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/30px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/40px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Goodbrother\" title=\"Gunthor Goodbrother\">Gunthor Goodbrother</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Strength</td></tr><tr><td>Unknown</td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faircastle\" title=\"Faircastle\">Faircastle</a> garrison</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Losses</td></tr><tr><td>Unknown</td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\">Hundreds of reavers<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Wynch\" title=\"Alester Wynch\">Alester Wynch</a>†</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a> a <b>rebellion</b> took place in <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a>, in the wake of the death of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>, the Red Kraken.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fair_Isle_rebellion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lord of the Iron Islands</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Reaper_of_Pyke\" title=\"Lord Reaper of Pyke\">Lord Reaper of Pyke</a>, seized <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the wake of Dalton's death in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, many <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> captains raced back to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>, as a <a href=\"/index.php/Struggle_for_power_in_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Struggle for power in the Iron Islands\">struggle for succession</a> was inevitable due to the Red Kraken's only heirs being <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_son\" title=\"Salt son\">salt sons</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> of the isle and the few <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> who remained on the island rose in rebellion against their ironmen oppressors. In the span of three days, hundreds of reavers were hacked to death or set upon on the docks, with their <a href=\"/index.php/Watercraft\" title=\"Watercraft\">ships</a> set ablaze.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ultimately, only <a href=\"/index.php/Faircastle\" title=\"Faircastle\">Faircastle</a> remained in the hands of the ironborn, with the garrison at the castle mostly composed of close companions of the late Dalton, led by <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Wynch\" title=\"Alester Wynch\">Alester Wynch</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Goodbrother\" title=\"Gunthor Goodbrother\">Gunthor Goodbrother</a>. The former was eventually killed by the latter in a quarrel over <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Farman\" title=\"Lysa Farman\">Lysa Farman</a>, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_wife\" title=\"Salt wife\">salt widows</a> of the Red Kraken.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>By the time Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a> arrived in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Velaryon_fleet\" title=\"Velaryon fleet\">Velaryon fleet</a>, Fair Isle was already free with the surviving ironborn having fled back to the Iron Islands in their longships.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fair_Isle_rebellion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Aegon III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Voyage of Alyn Oakenfist.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Wars_in_Westeros\" title=\"Template:Wars in Westeros\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:Wars_in_Westeros\" title=\"Template talk:Wars in Westeros\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Wars_in_Westeros&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nWars and rebellions in Westeros</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Before the Conquest</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_First_M